node.text:
Anytime I can make someone happy who does so much for others it lights me up!!!  

Big love to @amazonhome for helping me give back to a “Hometown Hero” whose dream was to give her home the love it deserved. Susanna is a rockstar special education teacher who has given so much of herself through the pandemic and has lost many loved ones so #amazonhome and I are giving Susanna a BIG surprise!! 
 
See the full transformation at amazon.com/hometownheroes and get in on this love Susanna deserves! 💜💜💜
 
AND @amazonhome also donated to my favorite orgs @keepachildalive @yourmomcares @breathewithmerevolution @untilfreedom
 
Today is a good day! 😘😘😘 #amazon #ad

This is going to blow your mind! Are u ready to try something that makes u totally uncomfortable? My 💜 @therealswizzz always says life begins at the end of your comfort zone. So, I’m inviting ya’ll to try this with me....Tell me how you feel after? 

There’s so many crazy triggers we have about our bodies and our physical appearance. Loving yourself as you are is a journey! So, so important!! Fill yourself up and #PraiseYourBody 

Can u see yourself doing this? 

Sending you Sunday blessings and love, always! 💜💜💜 @keyssoulcare

node.text:
This song “Foolish Heart” is the first song I recorded for what would eventually become Songs in A Minor 

I was 16 years old....

Stream it right now on Songs in A Minor 20th Edition 

Celebrating with you is everything!!!! I’m so grateful for each and everyone of YOU for going on this unimaginable journey with me. Thank you, thank you thank you, for the love, the powerful moments and all of your support. We are kindred! You mean more than the world to me. There is so much more to come! ✨✨✨

Big, endless, outrageous love to the #AKFAM we are forever intertwined! I adore you beyond words.

BEFORE Songs In A Minor came out 

This was for all the tastemakers, press, all the people they said could make or break her...

Was she nervous? Hell yea!!! So she resorted to jokes, that’s always been the best medicine for nerves

And Troubles has always been one of her favorite songs 💜💜

Which are yours? 

SIAM AK20 drops at midnight tomorrow with 2 unreleased songs. Wait until you hear this!!!

node.text:
When you look at your reflection what do you see? Do you see society’s standards of what you think you should be? 

Or do you actually see the magnificence of you? 

Praise your body 💜💜💜 

Give thanks for it standing with you, carrying you and making you exactly who you are.   If you wrote your body a love letter today, what would it say?
